    1  2  3             
    4  5  6
    7  8  9

after transpose, it will be swap(matrix[i][j], matrix[j][i])

    1  4  7
    2  5  8
    3  6  9

Then flip the matrix horizontally.  (swap(matrix[i][j], matrix[i][matrix.length-1-j])

    7  4  1
    8  5  2
    9  6  3

