Then we do the same for innner rings formed.
* For each ring/circle, we exchange elements clockwise and after we finish one circle, we can continue processing the next.

The process continues till the last ring has either 0 ```[for even length matrix]``` or 1```[for odd length matrix]``` elements left in centre.
