Variant V - Rotate Rectangular matrix by by 90 deg anti-clockwise / 270 deg clockwise (can't be done in place)

 1, 2, 3, 4            4, 8,12
 5, 6, 7, 8   =====>   3, 7,11
 9,10,11,12            2, 6,10
                       1, 5, 9
*/
