solutions.content:
My approach is to find the transpose of the given matrix and then reverse each individual vector with in 2d vector.
let us take one example and be clear.
suppose Given input matrix = 
[
  [1,2,3],
  [4,5,6],
  [7,8,9]
]
step 1: find the transpose of the matrix.
 after tranposing it looks something like this.
 [
 [1,4,7],
 [2,5,8],
 [3,6,9]
 ]
 step 2: reverse individual vectors with in 2d vector.
 [
 [7,4,1],
 [8,5,2],
 [9,6,3]
 ]
 This is our required answer.. 
 My code is as follows
```
class Solution {
public:
