# Sort List
**KNOCKCAT**
```
1. 2 Pointer Approach / Fast Slow (Turtle-Hare Algorithm) Finding the Middle Element.
2. Simple Merge Sort Logic , As we Handle in Case of Array.
3. Explanation as Comments.
